title: Zeit Remixed 3/9: LA Rams, Reggie, Max Von Sydow, Corona Virus: Ohio
itunes:title: Zeit Remixed 3/9: LA Rams, Reggie, Max Von Sydow, Corona Virus: Ohio
description:
On this edition of Zeit Remixed Jack, Miles, and DJ Danl discuss the new LA Rams logo, Reggie Fils Aime has reappeared in the space of video games by joining the board of Game Stop, lifelong actor Max Von Sydow has passed at the age of 90, and 3 cases of COVID-19 have popped up in Ohio.
